OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FHundreds of flights have been delayed
OL,7,Fand dozens more cancelled at London's
OL,8,FGatwick and Heathrow airports
OL,9,Ffollowing thunderstorms, with further
OL,10,Fdisruption expected.
OL,12,FOvernight downpours caused major
OL,13,Fdisruption at two of London's busiest
OL,14,Fairports on Saturday, with some people
OL,15,Fonline reporting being stuck on
OL,16,Fgrounded planes for several hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
