OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FAccording to flight tracker
OL,7,FFlightradar24, more than 400 flights
OL,8,Fat Gatwick have been delayed so far on
OL,9,FSaturday, with a further 96 cancelled,
OL,10,Fwhile nearly 600 flights at Heathrow
OL,11,Fhave been delayed and 119 cancelled.
OL,13,FBoth Heathrow and Gatwick told ITV
OL,14,FNews that adverse weather and
OL,15,Fthunderstorms overnight across the UK
OL,16,Fand Europe led to temporary air
OL,17,Ftraffic restrictions, affecting some
OL,18,Fflights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FThey urged those travelling to contact
OL,7,Ftheir airline for further information
OL,8,Fon their flights.
OL,10,FThe other UK airports remain largely
OL,11,Funaffected.
OL,13,FNATS, the UK's air traffic control
OL,14,Fservice, told ITV News that disruption
OL,15,Fis expected to continue for the
OL,16,Fremainder of Saturday and overnight
OL,17,Finto Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
