OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FIn a statement, NATS said: "Severe
OL,7,Fthunderstorms across the South East of
OL,8,FEngland and Europe continue to impact
OL,9,Fflights, and this is expected to
OL,10,Fcontinue for the remainder of today
OL,11,Fand overnight. To ensure the safety of
OL,12,Fthe travelling public, aircraft need
OL,13,Fto avoid affected areas and be spaced
OL,14,Ffurther apart, which limits the number
OL,15,Fof flights that can operate safely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
