CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,F"We understand disruption is
OL,7,Ffrustrating, but we're working closely
OL,8,Fwith airlines and airports to reduce
OL,9,Fdisruption as much as possible.
OL,10,FPassengers should continue to contact
OL,11,Ftheir airline for the latest
OL,12,Finformation on their flight."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FOne woman wrote on X that her British
OL,20,FAirways (BA) flight was delayed by
OL,21,Fmore than five hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
