OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FBA said in response the weather
OL,7,Fconditions in London were the reason
OL,8,Ffor the delays.
OL,10,FIn a statement, BA said: "Like other
OL,11,Fairlines, we've had to make some
OL,12,Fadjustments to our schedule today due
OL,13,Fto Air Traffic Control restrictions
OL,14,Fcaused by adverse weather conditions
OL,15,Faffecting parts of UK airspace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,F"While the majority of our customers
OL,7,Fwill be unaffected, we apologise for
OL,8,Fthe inconvenience caused and our teams
OL,9,Fare working hard to help those
OL,10,Fimpacted get their journeys back on
OL,11,Ftrack."
OL,13,FAnother woman took to social media to
OL,14,Fcomplain on her daughter's behalf. She
OL,15,Fsaid she had been sitting on a plane
OL,16,Fat Gatwick for four hours before the
OL,17,Fflight was cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
