OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FEasyJet told The Guardian it had to
OL,7,F"pre-emptively cancel some flights to
OL,8,Fand from Gatwick in advance" over the
OL,9,Fthunderstorms.
OL,11,F"We are doing all possible to minimise
OL,12,Fthe impact of the weather disruption
OL,13,Ffor our customers and are notifying
OL,14,Fpassengers in advance with their
OL,15,Foptions to rebook or receive a refund
OL,16,Fas well as hotel accommodation and
OL,17,Fmeals where required," a spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,FITV News has contacted easyJet for
OL,21,Fcomment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@\O]sD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
