OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FWizz Air said that "severe
OL,7,Fthunderstorms and hail across southern
OL,8,FUK airspace are causing significant
OL,9,Fdelays today", adding that some
OL,10,Fflights were being delayed.
OL,12,FThunderstorms developed across
OL,13,Fsoutheast England in the early hours
OL,14,Fof Saturday, following a record-
OL,15,Fbreaking June heatwave.
OL,17,FThe hottest ever June high of 37.3C
OL,18,Fwas recorded in Suffolk on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
