OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782616677
OL,3,CThunderstorms disrupt hundreds of
OL,4,Cflights at Gatwick and Heathrow
OL,6,FAn amber weather warning for extreme
OL,7,Fheat is in place until 9am on Sunday,
OL,8,Fwith the Met Office warning that very
OL,9,Fhot and humid weather will continue to
OL,10,Faffect eastern and southeastern
OL,11,FEngland. Temperatures are likely to be
OL,12,Fa few degrees cooler than the previous
OL,13,Ffew days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
